acceptance_criteria: Inventory GitHub reports and existing PR; validate all commands and documented output modes with real PM data; build/typecheck/test/pack/install/activate; inspect tarball; audit tracked files and full history; verify daily change-gated npm+Bun+GitHub release using pm-changelog; run Greptile; close all bot feedback and checks; merge and return main.
